<Action id="49950" issue="32501" author="yoni" type="comment" created="2018-09-06 05:20:37.0" updateauthor="yoni" updated="2018-09-06 05:20:37.0"> <body><! CDATA  ~mithun2679  see script below, you can play with the numbers to improve reproduction rate, the more pressure on the TP/validator the more likely to see the problem, on some iterations i saw the queue limit was down to 2  #!/bin/bash for((i=1;i<=10;++i)) do echo "loop iteration $i started" intkey workload --rate 10 -d 5 & sleep 15 kill -9 %%  intkey workload --rate 150 -d 2 & sleep 3 kill -9 %%  echo "loop iteration $i completed" done  ></body> </Action>
